293
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,060
Where's my father?

294
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:07,620
He and I are shopping out there.

295
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:08,900
We'll be back soon.

296
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:10,260
Where's he?

297
00:15:10,260 --> 00:15:11,740
Why didn't he answer the phone?

298
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:13,380
He's in the toilet.

299
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,660
I'm waiting out here.

300
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:16,660
Don't worry. He won't be lost.

301
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:18,980
I fear he'll run away.

302
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:21,500
He won't.

303
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:24,380
Don't scare yourself.

304
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:25,460
Help me to persuade him.

305
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:27,900
I've done everything I could

306
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:29,060
but failed to change his mind.

307
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:29,980
I'm trying.

308
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:30,780
Don't worry.

309
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:33,500
I'll let you know when I succeed.

310
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:34,940
Okay.

311
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:42,660
Han,

312
00:15:43,140 --> 00:15:44,620
I invited you over

313
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,580
because I wanted

314
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:48,580
to say sorry

315
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:51,500
as Jia Fan's father.

316
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:54,060
You know very well

317
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,060
about our family.

318
00:15:55,220 --> 00:15:56,700
I'm Jia Fan's burden.

319
00:15:57,420 --> 00:15:59,340
Because of me, he's had a hard time.

320
00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:01,660
Even you...

321
00:16:02,260 --> 00:16:03,420
You suffered, too.

322
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,700
That's right.

323
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:10,660
I've always been worried.

324
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:12,940
What if you get hurt?

325
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,740
What if you have an accident?

326
00:16:15,340 --> 00:16:16,860
It tortures me, indeed.

327
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,180
Uncle Jia,

328
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:26,220
since you know I worry about Jia Fan,

329
00:16:27,700 --> 00:16:28,300
don't you know

330
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:30,100
he also worries about you?

331
00:16:31,260 --> 00:16:32,660
When I worry about him,

332
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:34,060
I know what to do.

333
00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:35,420
But when he worries about you,

334
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:36,780
I can't do anything.

335
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,300
I'm just stuck being anxious.

336
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:43,100
So, if you really want to apologize,

337
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:45,900
have the operation.

338
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:48,780
Then, we'll both be relieved.

339
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:50,900
Han, I got you here

340
00:16:50,900 --> 00:16:52,500
because I wanted you to persuade him.

341
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,060
Then you get the wrong person.

342
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,580
He became a model for you.

343
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:58,620
He's been working so hard

344
00:16:58,620 --> 00:16:59,100
to make you

345
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:00,940
see his performance one day.

346
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,060
Now is your chance.

347
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,260
But you reject it

348
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:05,100
just because you feel guilty.

349
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,260
What about him?

350
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:08,780
How can he accept that without guilt?

351
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:09,780
Then what is the point

352
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:11,180
of his hard work?

353
00:17:20,260 --> 00:17:21,620
Sorry for this, Uncle Jia.

354
00:17:29,820 --> 00:17:30,780
Uncle Jia,

355
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,820
stop hesitating.

356
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:35,060
Don't you want to see

357
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:38,140
what I really look like?

358
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,140
Oh, girl.

359
00:17:56,220 --> 00:17:57,380
Destiny

360
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:58,580
is always fair.

361
00:17:59,060 --> 00:18:00,460
When something's taken away,

362
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:02,700
something else will be given.

363
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:06,980
My son suffered so much with me...

364
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,700
just to meet you.

365
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:16,380
I agree.

366
00:18:17,460 --> 00:18:18,500
So,

367
00:18:19,060 --> 00:18:20,420
have the operation soon.

368
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:22,060
When you can see again,

369
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:24,300
you'll know how lucky he is.

370
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:34,060
You know what?

371
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:35,700
He has my taste.

372
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:37,700
You're very much like his mother.

373
00:18:38,340 --> 00:18:39,220
He takes after me.

374
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:51,340
Getting off before it's dark?

375
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:54,780
It's dinner time.

376
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,260
I'll go home for dinner.

377
00:19:57,660 --> 00:19:59,340
What about you? Going to the office?

378
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:01,140
No.

379
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,700
I was walking around.

380
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:04,140
I just passed by.

381
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:10,820
Don't eat too much takeout food.

382
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:11,900
It's not healthy.

383
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,140
Then...

384
00:20:21,340 --> 00:20:22,220
Shall we eat together?

385
00:20:22,220 --> 00:20:23,220
Okay.

386
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:24,940
In your place or mine?

387
00:20:26,100 --> 00:20:26,900
Mine.

388
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,220
It's near.

389
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:29,060
Let's go.

390
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,260
You didn't drive, either?

391
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:40,300
I was walking around.

392
00:20:43,060 --> 00:20:44,340
My car is restricted today.

393
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:45,980
So, I thought

394
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:48,060
I could take a walk.

395
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:50,740
It's eco-friendly.

396
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:21,060
I told you not to buy so many things.

397
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:22,940
He's going to France,

398
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:24,580
not the moon.

399
00:21:24,860 --> 00:21:26,180
It doesn't matter.

400
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:27,340
The bread and sausage

401
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:28,500
aren't nutritious at all.

402
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:29,700
Who would want to eat them?

403
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:32,900
Pickles and instant noodles are sold.

404
00:21:33,620 --> 00:21:35,620
He'll pay a lot for excess luggage.

405
00:21:35,740 --> 00:21:36,580
Stop gibbering.

406
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:37,660
Do what I tell you.

407
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:39,260
Keep your mouth shut.

408
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:40,260
Don't tell him everything.

409
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:41,820
Or he'll be angry.

410
00:21:45,380 --> 00:21:46,100
Just remember.

411
00:21:46,100 --> 00:21:47,820
You must not tell Fan about this.

412
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:51,980
Move on.

413
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:54,340
If you keep saying, he'll know.

414
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:57,820
See?

415
00:21:58,380 --> 00:22:00,500
If you can see,
you won't be so embarrassed.

416
00:22:02,980 --> 00:22:04,060
Leave it to me.

417
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:05,540
I've been starving the whole day.

418
00:22:05,540 --> 00:22:06,780
I'll go have something to eat.

419
00:22:06,780 --> 00:22:07,620
You guys talk.

420
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:11,180
Hey, Dad.

421
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:12,580
What did you do?

422
00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:43,500
It tastes great.

423
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:46,700
Will you run a restaurant

424
00:22:47,300 --> 00:22:48,540
and be a chef?

425
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:02,140
A bad joke, huh?

426
00:23:17,340 --> 00:23:18,540
Thank you...

427
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:21,860
for Jia Fan.

428
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:28,460
I also did that for myself.

429
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:30,780
Especially for me.

430
00:23:36,260 --> 00:23:37,500
All these years...

431
00:23:39,860 --> 00:23:41,380
you've done a lot for me.

432
00:23:43,420 --> 00:23:44,460
I know everything.

433
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:49,140
Because we're the same.

434
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,100
Our bark is worse than our bite.

435
00:23:53,820 --> 00:23:55,540
We sacrifice everything for pride.

436
00:23:57,500 --> 00:23:58,700
In front of our families,

437
00:23:59,540 --> 00:24:00,780
we have to be strong.

438
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:04,100
So, we're tired.

439
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:12,540
People are born what they are.

440
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,620
They can't change.

441
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:17,660
We should at least try.

442
00:24:20,420 --> 00:24:22,620
At least in front of our families,

443
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:26,060
we don't need to be tough.

444
00:24:31,700 --> 00:24:32,820
Aunt.

445
00:24:37,420 --> 00:24:39,180
I also want to apologize.

446
00:24:43,060 --> 00:24:44,380
All these years...

447
00:24:46,020 --> 00:24:47,820
I've been misunderstanding you...

448
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:50,820
and breaking your heart.

449
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,420
I'm sorry.

450
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:04,900
And...

451
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:10,300
Thank you.

452
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:14,500
For taking me home.

453
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:46,940
Dad.

454
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:51,020
Stop feeling sorry for me.

455
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:54,220
Compared to my eyes,

456
00:25:55,460 --> 00:25:57,180
your apologies make me feel worse.

457
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:00,100
Fine.

458
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:04,420
I knew you could have my problem,

459
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:06,780
but I still had you.

460
00:26:07,940 --> 00:26:09,700
Or who'd take care of me when I was old?

461
00:26:14,700 --> 00:26:15,860
Yeah.

462
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:17,340
Or how could you have

463
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:18,540
such an excellent son?

464
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:21,300
Don't be as thick-skinned

465
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:23,300
as me.

466
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:25,020
I get everything from you.

467
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:26,660
A family should stick together.

468
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:28,460
We share everything for better or worse.

469
00:26:31,100 --> 00:26:31,980
Okay.

470
00:26:32,820 --> 00:26:33,860
Then I will

471
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:35,700
enjoy what you offer me.

472
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:38,180
I'll watch your show,

473
00:26:38,500 --> 00:26:39,780
live in your big house,

474
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:41,980
and go for a drive with Gold.

475
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,340
Even if I can't do these things,

476
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,340
I will at least

477
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:53,220
watch how hard you work.

478
00:26:55,340 --> 00:26:56,620
It must be cool.

479
00:27:04,380 --> 00:27:05,380
I want more.

480
00:27:07,780 --> 00:27:10,260
Before, I've never
looked at you so silently.

481
00:27:16,860 --> 00:27:18,620
Do you have any plans?

482
00:27:20,500 --> 00:27:22,300
We'll see.

483
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:25,420
In my opinion,

484
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:26,900
you can be whatever you want to be.

485
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:29,260
Even a chef.

486
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:35,140
So, do you think highly
of my cooking skills

487
00:27:35,420 --> 00:27:37,140
or do you want to invest?

488
00:27:40,020 --> 00:27:42,060
Good things are for the family.

489
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:44,460
You're Han Yijing.

490
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:46,020
You can do anything very well.

491
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:49,860
And you're my rich aunt.

492
00:27:51,980 --> 00:27:53,620
You'll have an investment priority.

493
00:27:53,620 --> 00:27:54,940
I'll take charge of anything else.

494
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:57,620
Whatever you say.

495
00:27:58,700 --> 00:28:00,500
I tried so many times to persuade you,

496
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:02,860
but it never worked.

497
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:04,980
Yijing tried once.

498
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:06,700
Only once.

499
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:08,660
Listen.

500
00:28:08,660 --> 00:28:10,340
You should cherish her.

501
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:12,220
Marry her when you're back from abroad.

502
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:15,940
You didn't tell her, huh?

503
00:28:16,740 --> 00:28:18,020
I'm not that silly.

504
00:28:18,020 --> 00:28:19,620
You should say it yourself.

505
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:22,380
Fine.

506
00:28:22,620 --> 00:28:23,980
I know what to do.

507
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:28,020
If your mother could see this,

508
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:31,220
she would be delighted.

509
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:38,380
When you have the operation,

510
00:28:40,420 --> 00:28:42,220
you'll know how delighted Mom would be.

511
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:14,500
[Qingning Hengtai Hospital]
I'm not nervous.

512
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:15,460
I've traveled everywhere

513
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:16,860
and seen everything.

514
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:18,020
You sound like a kid.

515
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:18,940
There you are.

516
00:29:19,660 --> 00:29:20,620
Hi. Thanks for it.

517
00:29:20,620 --> 00:29:21,460
Come back, Dad.

518
00:29:21,460 --> 00:29:23,060
How could you be late for this?

519
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:24,540
Everything is ready. Hurry.

520
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:25,620
Let's go.

521
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:26,620
Hi, boss.

522
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,260
Who's that?

523
00:29:27,260 --> 00:29:28,300
My boss.

524
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:29,460
Sorry for the trouble.

525
00:29:29,460 --> 00:29:30,220
Come on.

526
00:29:34,380 --> 00:29:35,140
Don't worry, Dad.

527
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:36,020
It's no problem.

528
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,700
He'll be able to see again.

529
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,820
So, you got up early and put on makeup?

530
00:29:45,140 --> 00:29:46,300
He'll see me for the first time.

531
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,100
I should make a good impression.

532
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,700
Hey, Mei.

533
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:09,380
What's up?

534
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:11,220
I heard you'd have a blind date.

535
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,500
Really?

536
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:13,620
Can you give me a chance?

537
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:15,780
How dare you try to get me?

538
00:30:17,180 --> 00:30:18,140
I'd take anyone over you.

539
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,300
If you come again, I'll kill you!

540
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:22,460
♪Wait until the clouds disperse♪

541
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:26,180
