543
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:29,620
I heard she was a model.

544
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,260
For real?

545
00:30:30,260 --> 00:30:31,220
♪Your skirt in the sunlight♪

546
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,660
♪Is as bright as your smile♪

