00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:11,740
♪Chasing stars takes great courage♪

561
00:31:12,580 --> 00:31:14,860
♪Wait until the clouds disperse♪

562
00:31:14,860 --> 00:31:18,380
♪The wind blows past us naturally♪

563
00:31:19,100 --> 00:31:20,660
♪Let it flow♪

564
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:23,740
♪Your skirt in the sunlight♪

565
00:31:24,020 --> 00:31:26,860
♪Is as bright as your smile♪

566
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:28,380
I'm not going.

567
00:31:29,380 --> 00:31:30,860
♪All that's good♪

568
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:31,860
♪Around me, around me♪

569
00:31:32,620 --> 00:31:34,300
♪Welcome, welcome♪

570
00:31:34,740 --> 00:31:35,260
♪Forget your troubles♪

571
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,060
No way.

572
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,220
You have to go.

573
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:40,060
The Best Supporting Actress.

574
00:31:40,500 --> 00:31:42,020
Why am I always the sidekick?

575
00:31:42,020 --> 00:31:42,780
You have no idea.

576
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:45,300
That's part of getting a leading role.

577
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:47,020
And you weren't just nominated.

578
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:48,220
You've won the prize.

579
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,100
Is that so?

580
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:52,900
Then, I can't go.

581
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:54,300
I'm going to Turkey.

